### C. Multiple dispatch preview

Multiple dispatch is one of Julia’s signature features, and the official site highlights it heavily. You do not need it yet, but here is the idea: the method Julia uses can depend on the types of the arguments. ([The Julia Programming Language][1])

```julia
describe(x::Int) = println("Integer")
describe(x::String) = println("String")

describe(5)
describe("hello")
```

